spirit:component.spirit:name: v_scaler_0
spirit:component.spirit:description: The Xilinx Video Scaler LogicCORE is spatially scales video streams in real time. It supports all SD and HD resolutions. It is implemented as a polyphase filter that supports 2-12 H/V taps with programmable coefficients. The user may select either a parameterizable dynamically-configurable AXI4-Lite netlist or a Constant interface netlist. The AXI4-Lite core enables a microprocessor or external state-machine to program scaler parameters and load coefficient sets in real time.
